  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together olive oil, lemon juice, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the minced garlic to the bowl and mix well.",
    "Brush the garlic mixture onto both sides of the Portobello mushrooms.",
    "Place the mushrooms on the grill and cook for 4 minutes per side, or until tender.",
    "While the mushrooms are cooking, toss the blueberries with a little bit of olive oil and place them on the grill for 2-3 minutes, or until slightly charred.",
    "Once the mushrooms are done, remove them from the grill and top each one with a few blueberries.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
